JWT 101 - a simple node JWT api authentication

This is a boilerplate project for study purposes - it will continue to grow to achieve some features in the future

For now, what it has is:
* Simple routing with middlewares for user creation and authentication
* Ready for MongoDB Atlas integration with mongoose
* Usage of bcrypt

Based on Dev Ed's tutorial at https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2jqok-WgelI <- be sure to check it out!